{"lastModified":1775041809814,"uri":"c::19057481779::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"This Lagoon 50 catamaran, based in Athens, is perfect for exploring the Saronic Gulf and the Cyclades. \nOn board, guests are looked after by an experienced captain who knows the area well, and a hostess who prepares traditional Mediterranean cuisine.\n\nThe yacht has 6 double cabins and 4 bathrooms, offering plenty of space for comfort and relaxation.\n\nFor fun on the water, it is fully equipped with a tender with 30 hp, a Seascooter, 1 Sub, snorkeling equipment, beach toys, fishing gear, 1 large tube, and water skiing for kids.\n\nThis Lagoon 50 is ideal for guests looking for a comfortable, fun, and enjoyable multi-day charter in Greece","blueprint":{"name":"SOPHIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::03842240-3c65-11f0-b692-115cd0cd6b28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::03b173d0-3c65-11f0-b692-115cd0cd6b28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::f549b6f0-17be-11f1-a478-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::f54a0510-17be-11f1-a478-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::03c63450-3c65-11f0-b5ff-d77f93113f5d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::03850ca0-3c65-11f0-a434-2556504e867f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::03af29e0-3c65-11f0-8536-53bdfff6b6d1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::0388dd30-3c65-11f0-8452-39e4e9c32881/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e7455840-3a0e-11f0-8892-61970e8f798b::assets::